Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有听到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果落下去了  在这样的暴风雨救上来是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还只是个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么简单的放弃我
