Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天有暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有很大的家伙
