Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这种时候最后的手段是…
