Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什什什什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是地狱  这是…天国…
