Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好重  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这个那个都偷懒不工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是男孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子会变得很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  没关…不会没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不单救了我  连饭都准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫东方院行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃不喝一周漂流到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连你也在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还以为漂流到了相当远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好还是在日本里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实住在这里的都是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这岛在哪里可不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为  其实我们也是漂流到了这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是距现在130年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本开国后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了学习最新的技术和医学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驶向欧洲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆您贵庚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是途中碰到大风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然就漂流到了这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庆幸的是这个岛容易居住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,取了和沉没的船一样的名字  叫蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样生活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还有这样的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看你身穿的装饰  日本也改变的相当的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有离开岛的船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样怎么才能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在别想多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在铃家里慢慢的养伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后的事情以后考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用船到附近的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里也许会有联络船或飞机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  刚才就在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时让你睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上让你好好吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在很忙  没空和你玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别把人说的好像很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要住在铃家比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃家非常的破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屋顶破了会漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有虫子老鼠一堆堆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  铃睡相很差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还会尿床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种差劲的攻击  对我是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么走吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以吗  那样放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度  绫音没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故意被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在后面  找寻敌人的破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中我的计谋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这回吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然身体还麻痹着  还过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给  解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多被打中几次就会习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不想习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音她从小就和我针锋相对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事就来找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我是否愿意这一点  还真为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说起来  你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家双亲都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  问了不该问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还真为难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和女孩一起  两人同住一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行  不能想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那么我也进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…铃…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  帮你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…我已经洗过了  不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢大家相互搓背了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相互搓背？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平常女生能无所谓的和男生一起进浴室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人  舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许就是岛上的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,这回轮到行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样我也平静的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从哪里冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想来擦洗行人大人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到每一寸肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那由我来做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  像你这样的小鬼  真的能让男士满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说小鬼还真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音你也不是又矮又平的  像小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不得不和你做一回了断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  热得晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  冷水拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:36.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来带你参观这个岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事无所谓  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  公子  还真危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  绫音那家伙竟然偷跑  还真不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是木匠玲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说回来  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  那个  我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做我的丈…丈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  为什么这么简单的事情说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是漂流到岛上的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子…我可不想被小孩子说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把淑女说成小孩是侮辱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃深受打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要  不要  不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  作为赔礼  今天和雪乃约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  那边的公子是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这早熟的小鬼  还早十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是雪乃的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不逃的话  就要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要尽快离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你准备的很丰盛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着铃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说被绑架出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎感觉到了杀气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你在为难什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还是白天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我叫千影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…感觉很懂礼貌  这是个正常的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一样的手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,躲过了我的吹箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是不同的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  连射式？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有趣的研究对象  可不能让你逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊  上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家都要追着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人是婆婆叫我照看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是这样说  你却是想自己独占男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想和铃一样跟他约会  亲热什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:04.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那种事情没做过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亲热又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  大家这么围着人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这岛到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这岛上没有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除你以外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这全是女人的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就我一个男的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有几条命都不够的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然铃照顾了我许多  但我还是决定要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追我追的那么厉害的人  还真这么容易就放我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝兰岛吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然受了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看还真是美丽的岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗  让他走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让他自身体验是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这岛的周围都被漩涡所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到不了外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想从我的手里逃出去是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…头冒星星  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仅靠自己要出这岛是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么努力绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行的  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去做过怎么会知道！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想做的话  先把我打倒了再去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然做不到的话  就别说大话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的「绝对不行」已经罗嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我会死心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么试都没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你超越不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人  要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说是绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要做了比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样乱来下去  不单单只是受重伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只看出我到现在都被打飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我有好好的用身体记住漩涡的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么失败  人所做的事情没有一样是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是爷爷的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经看穿这一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的已经完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢做无意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认真倔强的男人真是不讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连什么是男人都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会成功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  那边不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  如我所想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡和漩涡之间有间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈～  看到了吗  这回是我的胜利…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虎…虎鲸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这家伙是来妨碍我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  一个又一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想做什么的时候总会有碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经忍不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样受别人做主的人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想打到你～的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好运  现在的话能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  已经没有力气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来…了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果…我还是什么都没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这深海里  成为虎鲸的饲料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是来救我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生鱼片是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些漩涡外面的地方  有最大的激流漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且任何东西都会被卷裂  吸入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生鱼片是为了不让任何人接近而巡视着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说不能离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是行人很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎也被感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像到现在为止都没有像这样全力贯彻自己的想法到底的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉轻松了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,透明了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.06,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,「被围追的  女婿殿下」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样这个岛也得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  行人  振作一点
